fields.name: title
fields.descr: "A short title used to represent this page in navigational structures such as table of contents, bread crumbs, etc."

fields.name: kind
fields.descr: "The kind of page that this is. Some pages are autogenerated (list, example), and other kinds are of interest so that tools can navigate the user to the page of interest."

fields.name: type
fields.descr: "For constructed pages, what kind of resources to include in the list."

fields.name: FHIRpackage
fields.descr: "For constructed pages, a list of packages to include in the page (or else empty for everything)."
